@startuml Withdrawal_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: Withdrawal Request Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Withdrawal Request State Transitions

[*] --> Initiated : Researcher requests withdrawal

Initiated --> Validating : Check balance & limits
Validating --> Approved : Validation passed
Validating --> Rejected : Validation failed

Rejected --> [*]

Approved --> Processing : Send to payment gateway
Processing --> Gateway_Pending : Awaiting gateway response
Gateway_Pending --> Completed : Transfer successful
Gateway_Pending --> Failed : Transfer failed

Failed --> Retry_Scheduled : Auto-retry enabled
Retry_Scheduled --> Processing : Retry attempt
Retry_Scheduled --> Refunded : Max retries exceeded

Refunded --> [*]
Completed --> [*]

note right of Validating
  Checks:
  - Sufficient balance
  - Minimum amount
  - Daily/monthly limits
  - Account verified
end note

note right of Gateway_Pending
  Payment Gateways:
  - Telebirr
  - CBE Birr
  - Bank Transfer
end note

note right of Failed
  Failure reasons:
  - Invalid account
  - Gateway timeout
  - Insufficient funds
  - Network error
end note

@enduml